# ─── SMTP Configuration (Google Workspace) ────────────────────────────────────
# Required for the /api/contact route to email form submissions to support@braneiq.com
# The app always uses smtp.gmail.com:587 — you only need to set these two values.
#
# HOW TO GET YOUR APP PASSWORD (Google Workspace):
#   1. Sign in to admin.google.com → Security → 2-Step Verification → enable it
#   2. Go to myaccount.google.com → Security → App passwords
#   3. Create an app password for "Mail" on "Other (custom)" → name it "BraneIQ Website"
#   4. Copy the 16-character password Google generates — paste it as SMTP_PASS below
#
# In production these values come from GitHub Secrets (SMTP_USER, SMTP_PASS)
# and are written to /var/www/braneiq-web/.env on the EC2 server by deploy.yml.

# Your Google Workspace email address used to send
SMTP_USER=support@braneiq.com

# The 16-character App Password generated in Google Account → Security → App passwords
SMTP_PASS=xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx
